6. Pipes

Description:
Pipes validate or transform input before it reaches the controller.

Use case:
Validate body data or convert route params.

@Get(':id')
findOne(@Param('id', ParseIntPipe) id: number) {
  return this.usersService.findById(id);
}

Global validation:

app.useGlobalPipes(
  new ValidationPipe({
    whitelist: true,
    transform: true,
    forbidNonWhitelisted: true,
  }),
);

